OL,3,CUkraine-Russia talks postponed as
OL,4,CMiddle East war draws attention away
OL,6,FA new round of US-brokered talks
OL,7,Fbetween Russia and Ukraine planned for
OL,8,Fthis week has been postponed as
OL,9,Fconflict in the Middle East draws
OL,10,Fattention away from the war in Europe,
OL,11,FUkrainian President Volodymyr
OL,12,FZelenskyy.
OL,14,F"Right now, because of the situation
OL,15,Faround Iran, there are not yet the
OL,16,Fnecessary signals for a trilateral
OL,17,Fmeeting," Zelenskyy said late on
OL,18,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
