PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772744765
OL,3,CUkraine-Russia talks postponed as
OL,4,CMiddle East war draws attention away
OL,6,F"But as soon as the security situation
OL,7,Fand the overall political context
OL,8,Fallow us to resume that trilateral
OL,9,Fdiplomatic work, it will be done."
OL,11,FHis comments come as the United States
OL,12,Fand its Middle Eastern allies are
OL,13,Fseeking Kyiv's expertise in countering
OL,14,FIran's Shahed drones, which the
OL,15,FIslamic Republic has been supplying to
OL,16,FRussia.
OL,26,@qD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
