OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772744765
OL,3,CUkraine-Russia talks postponed as
OL,4,CMiddle East war draws attention away
OL,6,FRussia has fired tens of thousands of
OL,7,FShaheds at Ukraine since it invaded
OL,8,Fits neighbour just over four years
OL,9,Fago, and Iran has been using the same
OL,10,Ftype of drones as it retaliates to
OL,11,Fjoint US-Israeli strikes.
OL,13,FZelenskyy said he has spoken in recent
OL,14,Fdays about possible cooperation with
OL,15,Fthe leaders of the United Arab
OL,16,FEmirates, Qatar, Bahrain, Jordan and
OL,17,FKuwait ` Gulf state allies of the US
OL,18,Fwho have seen facilities targeted by
OL,19,FIran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
