OL,3,CUkraine-Russia talks postponed as
OL,4,CMiddle East war draws attention away
OL,6,FUkrainian assistance, he said, will be
OL,7,Fprovided only if it does not weaken
OL,8,FUkraine's own defences and if it adds
OL,9,Fleverage to Kyiv's diplomatic efforts
OL,10,Fto stop the Russian invasion.
OL,12,F"We help to defend from war those who
OL,13,Fhelp us, Ukraine, bring a just end to
OL,14,Fthe war" with Russia, Zelenskyy said.
