OL,3,CUkraine-Russia talks postponed as
OL,4,CMiddle East war draws attention away
OL,6,FUkraine's army has recently pushed
OL,7,Fback Russian forces at some points
OL,8,Falong the roughly 1,250-kilometer
OL,9,Ffront line, according to the Institute
OL,10,Ffor the Study of War.
OL,12,FLocalised Ukrainian counterattacks
OL,13,Fliberated more territory than
OL,14,FUkrainian forces lost in the last two
OL,15,Fweeks of February, the Washington-
OL,16,Fbased think tank said this week.
OL,18,FIt estimates that about 257 square
OL,19,Fkilometres of land have been recovered
OL,20,Fsince January 1.
